name: VFox
desc: Join the VFox Alliance ! This collection is made of 4,999 VFox NFTs. VFoxes are kind and brave shinobis ready to defend VFoxia against the threat of the mysterious Undead. They are made of +180 variations, including their fur and weapons. Among them are hidden 9 unique warriors and 45 Undead. We must react quickly and unite VFox tribes to ensure that peace prevails!
